{"BUZZ":[{"def":"To make a low, continuous, humming or sibilant sound, like that made by bees with their wings.","pos":""}],"BUZZARD":[{"def":"A bird of prey of the Hawk family, belonging to the genus Buteo and related genera.","pos":"noun"}],"BUZZARDET":[{"def":"A hawk resembling the buzzard, but with legs relatively longer.","pos":""}],"BUZZER":[{"def":"One who, or that which, buzzes; a whisperer; a talebearer.","pos":""}],"BUZZINGLY":[{"def":"In a buzzing manner; with a buzzing sound.","pos":""}],"BUZZSAW":[{"def":"A circular saw; -- so called from the buzzing it makes when running at full speed.","pos":""}]}